 null, "type": "select", "label": "Operation", "help": "", "help_format": "html", "refresh_on_change": true, "optional": false, "hidden": false, "is_dynamic": false, "value": "bounding_box_query", "options": [["Query a SpatialData object or SpatialElement within a bounding box. (sd.bounding_box_query)", "bounding_box_query", false], ["Query a SpatialData object or a SpatialElement by a polygon or multipolygon. (sd.polygon_query)", "polygon_query", false], ["Get the values from the element, from any location: df columns, obs or var columns (table). (sd.get_values)", "get_values", false], ["Get the instances (index values) of the SpatialElement. (sd.get_element_instances)", "get_element_instances", false], ["Get the extent (bounding box) of a SpatialData object or a SpatialElement. (sd.get_extent)", "get_extent", false], ["Get the centroids of the geometries contained in a SpatialElement, as a new Points element. (sd.get_centroids)", "get_centroids", false], ["Perform SQL like joins of SpatialElements and a table. (sd.join_spatialelement_table)", "join_spatialelement_table", false], ["Filter the elements and make the indices match those in the table. (sd.match_element_to_table)", "match_element_to_table", false], ["Filter the table and reorders the rows to match the instances (rows/labels) of the specified SpatialElement. (sd.match_table_to_element)", "match_table_to_element", false], ["Filter the elements of a SpatialData object to match only the rows present in the table. (sd.match_sdata_to_table)", "match_sdata_to_table", false], ["Filter the SpatialData object based on a set of table queries. (sd.filter_by_table_query)", "filter_by_table_query", false], ["Concatenate a list of spatial data objects (sd.concatenate)", "concatenate", false], ["Transform a SpatialElement using the transformation to a coordinate system, and returns the transformed element. (sd.transform)", "transform", false], ["Rasterize a SpatialData object or a SpatialElement (image, labels, points, shapes). (sd.rasterize)", "rasterize", false], ["Rasterizes grid-like binned shapes/points annotated by a table (e.g. Visium HD data). (sd.rasterize_bins)", "rasterize_bins", false], ["Change the annotation target of the table to the rasterized labels. (sd.rasterize_bins_link_table_to_labels)", "rasterize_bins_link_table_to_labels", false], ["Convert a set of geometries (2D/3D labels, 2D shapes) to approximated circles/spheres. (sd.to_circles)", "to_circles", false], ["Convert a set of geometries (2D labels, 2D shapes) to approximated 2D polygons/multypolygons. (sd.to_polygons)", "to_polygons", false], ["Aggregate values by given region. (sd.aggregate)", "aggregate", false], ["Apply a callable to raster data. (sd.map_raster)", "map_raster", false], ["Remove padding from a raster type that was eventually added by the rotation component of a transformation. (sd.unpad_raster)", "unpad_raster", false], ["Check if two data extents, as returned by get_extent() are equal up to approximation errors. (sd.are_extents_equal)", "are_extents_equal", false], ["Sanitize all keys in an AnnData table to comply with SpatialData naming rules. (sd.sanitize_table)", "sanitize_table", false], ["Export the table of a SpatialData object to anndata", "export_table", false], ["Import anndata table to a SpatialData object", "import_table", false], ["Add a shape to a SpatialData object", "add_shape", false]], "display": null, "multiple": false, "textable": false}}], "outputs": [{"model_class": "ToolOutput", "name": "spatialdata_output", "format": "spatialdata.zip", "label": "${tool.name} on ${on_string}: ${operation_condi.operation}", "hidden": false, "output_type": "data", "format_source": null, "default_identifier_source": "None", "metadata_source": null, "parent": null, "count": 1, "from_work_dir": "spatialdata.spatialdata.zip", "edam_format": "format_2333", "edam_data": "data_0006", "discover_datasets": []}, {"model_class": "ToolOutput", "name": "result_tabular", "format": "tabular", "lab